Input
# Task 1: Books and authors
books = {
    "To Kill a Mockingbird": "Harper Lee",
    "1984": "George Orwell",
    "Pride and Prejudice": "Jane Austen",
    "The Great Gatsby": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
    "Moby Dick": "Herman Melville"
}
print("Books and authors:")
print("To Kill a Mockingbird by", books["To Kill a Mockingbird"])
print("1984 by", books["1984"])
print("Pride and Prejudice by", books["Pride and Prejudice"])
print("The Great Gatsby by", books["The Great Gatsby"])
print("Moby Dick by", books["Moby Dick"])
print()

Output:

Books and authors:
To Kill a Mockingbird by Harper Lee
1984 by George Orwell
Pride and Prejudice by Jane Austen
The Great Gatsby by F. Scott Fitzgerald
Moby Dick by Herman Melville
